---
description: "Rules for working on Kubernetes controller reconciliation logic"
globs: ["internal/controller/**/*.go"]
---

- The reconciler struct is `MetricsConfigReconciler`
- `collectPromStats()` and `configurePVC()` are package-level functions, not reconciler methods
- Handle `apierrors.IsNotFound(err)` gracefully -- return `ctrl.Result{}, nil` for deleted resources
- Use `ctrl.LoggerFrom(ctx)` for structured logging
- Prefer updating CR status via `updateStatusAndLogError()` after state changes; use direct `r.Status().Update(...)` only when the code path intentionally aggregates/returns update errors
